{"id":282437,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-两会期间长沙李香等15位访民在京旅游遭遣/","date":"2013-03-06T04:15:43Z","modified":"2013-03-06T04:15:43Z","title":"维权网 | 两会期间长沙李香等15位访民在京旅游遭遣返（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员李军报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，长沙访民李香、吴莎、段静玲等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>人在北京天安门旅游，刚下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>路车，就被天安门公安检查身份证，随后众人被警察带到了天安门分局，李香、吴莎等遭到警察搜包检查，天安门分局警察</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">051542</span><span>查看吴莎的手机，要求吴莎把手机里的相片都删掉。</span>  </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>随后天安门分局的警察用车将众人带到马家楼，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日晚上八点</span><span>到达马家楼，马家楼工作人员问你们是干吗的，大家说是旅游的，马家楼工作人员说，旅游的来这干吗。众访民说我们又不要来，是天安门警察强行拐来的，让我们出门自己走回去。随后吴莎拔打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>要大家在车上不要下来，车上有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>人，其中有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60-70</span><span>岁的老人，有心脏病，高血压，冠心</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>报警半小时后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>警察</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">040367</span><span>刘警官过来了，问了情况后，要大家千万不要下车，他去请示领导，然后让大家去打水喝，车上还有几个老人没吃饭没水吃药。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>随后有长沙驻京办人员把车包围了，来了一些黑保安，长沙市芙蓉区东牌楼拆迁指挥部的姓彭男子在车下记录众访民的姓名。长沙市芙蓉区解放路定王台街道办事处政法委书记杨斌也来到现场。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>位访民有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>个小时没吃饭了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当晚，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>位访民又被转移到了久敬庄，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日长沙天心区的访民被当地政府集中派车遣返回长沙，其他乘火车返回。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ixe8QvH53WY/UTa9Dj9A2lI/AAAAAAAAeaU/b9znqcGRjCI/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ixe8QvH53WY/UTa9Dj9A2lI/AAAAAAAAeaU/b9znqcGRjCI/s400/1.jpg\" width=\"335\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XpHAt7adjGE/UTa9BiMJ9XI/AAAAAAAAeac/_BR4T6oRCsQ/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XpHAt7adjGE/UTa9BiMJ9XI/AAAAAAAAeac/_BR4T6oRCsQ/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"281\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-zr_IK1fOoUc/UTa9DWg6TgI/AAAAAAAAeak/fd9ehHIWrC0/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-zr_IK1fOoUc/UTa9DWg6TgI/AAAAAAAAeak/fd9ehHIWrC0/s400/3.jpg\" width=\"272\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}